Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! Who are you?\NAnd I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into\Nmy hospital, your name was Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:13.98,Title,Episode Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,350)\fad(1021,918)}House of Tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer! Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner! It's Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... I mean,\NI've brought Nina home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call the police from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.02,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like\Nthe police ever came...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.59,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Come back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come back to life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...\NYour favorite cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... killed... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him... I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.\N— But that day, I killed my brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I brought him back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line has been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get\Naway from here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police.\NWe received a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind,\Nwe'll have a look around inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right? Any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank heavens.\NWe'll have help soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take care of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear your stories\Ndown at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the victims' daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that means\Nyou didn't see who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To think something like that could\Nhappen in such a peaceful town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? China?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm Japanese.\NMy name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible experience for you\Nin such a faraway land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady... You're all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Heidelberg Police Department\Nis in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Mannheim Precinct\Nin the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.29,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I wonder why they're taking us\Nto the next precinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be there in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:50.34,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,He said they got a call...\NThey came because they got a call...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.57,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Who could have called them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.38,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,The phone line was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.48,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,This car came without sirens blaring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.49,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Would the police whisk away\Nthe people who discovered the bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.29,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,without first securing the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:11.56,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Still, those police IDs\Nlooked authentic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.01,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.01,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:28.82,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,It couldn't be that these men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A roadblock...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.05,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're searching for\Na hit-and-run driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'd appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Detective Mesner\Nand Detective Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... See you're doing your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on your way\Nback to headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a new car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,— How nice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.66,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,— What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a junk heap in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you don't take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl says she doesn't feel well.\NCan we go out and get some air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those two do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.86,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NAre they really detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:55.53,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,But what about that blood...?\NWhose call did they receive...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.20,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,They didn't even turn on their siren...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.24,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,What should we do? What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is everything all right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you my name,\Nbut I didn't tell you that I was a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a grocery story nearby.\NI even found some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's bread, sausage and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had them pour\Nsome coffee into this thermos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not have any appetite,\Nbut you've got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you'd better change\Nyour clothes. You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of dead people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and I walked among them,\Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like... we were the only people\Nleft in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?\NCan't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We crossed the border...\NA man and and his wife cheered us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my brother said that\Nhe had a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The man and his wife died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone who's ever\Nbeen nice to us... all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, I discovered\Nthe reason why... That rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about\NMr. and Mrs. Liebert, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother shot them...\NMy brother killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed them all up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took the gun...\NI aimed it at my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed as he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me,\Nthrow the gun outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure you shoot me in the head.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him like he said...\NI aimed for his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my mom and dad\Nwouldn't have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move from this place.\NI'll go to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the detectives last night\Nwere the real thing, that means that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,someone in the police department\Nis on Johan's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't just stay here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is trying to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hide\Nif someone comes looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat,\Ndrink some hot coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then sleep for a while...\NThat's how people go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive...\NYou must think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,100,,Don't you have any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:18.96,Monster - Time and Place,Time/Place,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,450)\fad(275,252)}Heidelberg Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,100,,Is there any connection to the string
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.40,Default,,0,0,100,,of killings of middle-age couples\Nthroughout Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, we are putting all of\Nour resources into this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not free to\Ndisclose any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have found that\NMr. and Mrs. Fortner have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is under investigation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was that newspaper reporter,\NMaurer, with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that Japanese guy\Nwho is said to have been with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese? He sounds suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that murder at Heidelberg Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred at nearly the same time,\Nthe work of the same killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.04,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Heidelberg Castle...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was killed, as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we will keep you\Nabreast of the happenings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Please let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough for an article!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I appreciate the help offered\Nby the Mannheim police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectives Mesner and Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give us our orders.\NWe'll do all we can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the investigations\Ncoming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about it inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.58,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,They're real...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.09,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Those guys are really\Nwith the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.22,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,What should I do...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heidelberg Post...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can't hear you!\NThe editing room is in chaos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N— At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you...?\N— we have to find that Japanese guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who was with Maurer!\NHe knows something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please quiet down! I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring an important witness\Nto your office at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not let the police know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!\NThis isn't a hoax, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:22.41,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,If I can't trust the police,\Nthere's only the paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:25.49,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,that can... keep Nina safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be in here\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're here from\Nthe federal police to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the killings of the middle-age couples,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have files on\Nthe killing at the castle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Something was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The case you're looking at and\Nthis one happened at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be the same perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy... It looks like there are signs\Nthat his hands had been tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find rope or anything nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It had been removed\Nby the time the victim was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.87,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,There are four possible routes\Nof escape from the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.56,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,He had to consider whether\Nhe'd be hidden from sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.10,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,how crowded the area was\Nwhere he'd come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.38,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,and the locations of the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, it's me... It's Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! You needn't hide anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...! Nina...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Nina...!! Nina...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... Was she taken away...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just did what you\Nhad to do as a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches\Nand get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to survive,\Nand save as many people as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.38,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Nina... What do you intend to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.71,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,Do you intend to try to\NKill him again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:16.52,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I brought him back to life...\NThat monster... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:22.23,Monster - Thoughts,Inner Dialogue,0,0,0,,I brought him back to life...
